title: Men of War Assault Squad 2 Ostfront Veteranen MULTi7-PLAZA
description:
P-R-E-S-E-N-T-S

Men of War: Assault Squad 2 - Ostfront Veteranen MULTi7
(c) 1C Entertainment

Release Date: 10/2018 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Action
Men of War: Assault Squad 2 Ostfront Veteranen is a new faction DLC
for the critically acclaimed RTS series and expands on the game with
a new unit selection, unseen in the franchise so far. Join the
battle as a new German faction with more than 10 new vehicles and
experienced infantry squads, who earned their spurs on the toughest
of all battlefields, the Eastern Front

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/920840/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
5. Play!

NOTES: This release is standalone updated to v3.261.0 and includes
the following DLC:

>Men of War: Assault Squad 2 - Deluxe Edition Content
>Men of War: Assault Squad 2 - Men of War Origins
>Men of War: Assault Squad 2 - Iron Fist
>Men of War: Assault Squad 2 - Airborne

>Men of War: Assault Squad 2 - Ostfront Veteranen
